snippet.title: WASHI YO WASHI - They Call Him OG | Pawan Kalyan | Emraan Hashmi | Sujeeth | Thaman S | Dvv Danayya
snippet.description:
The wait is worth it ‚ù§Ô∏è‚Äçüî•

#WashiYoWashi in the thunderous voice of Pawan Kalyan üí•

#OG #TheyCallHimOG

Music : Thaman S
Singer - Pawan Kalyan 

Programmed & arranged by - thaman S 
Song Programmed by - Roshan Vishal
NAKODA & Japanese drums - Sivamani 
Additional TAIKOS & Hokkaido drums - - Beyond Sound (T) 
Vocal Supervision - Thaman S & Sujeeth

Recorded by - Thaman S @ Vibe ( HYD )

Mix and Mastered by Shadab Rayeen @ New Edge ( Mumbai )
Assistant engineers - Jazbaat, Sohamm, Prasad

Musicians Co Ordinator - Manikandan K
Studio Manager - Seenu & Sridhar
Studio Assistance - Raju, Kannan, Lingam & Pawan

Cast - Pawan Kalyan, Emraan Hashmi, Priyanka Arul Mohan, Arjun Das, Sriya Reddy, Prakash Raj

Movie Name: They Call Him OG
Written & Directed by Sujeeth
Music by Thaman S
Production: DVV Entertainment
Presented by: Smt D.Parvathi
Produced by DVV Danayya, Kalyan Dasari
Cinematographers : Ravi K Chandran (ISC), Manoj Paramahamsa (ISC)
Production Designer : AS Prakash
Editor: Navin Nooli
Costume Designers: Darshan Jalan & Neelanchal Kumar Ghosh
Creative Director : Ashwin Mani
Creative Producer : Harish Pai
Action Masters : A Vijay, Peter Hein, Dhilip Subbarayan, Kevin Kumar, Stunt Silva, Sunil Rodrigues, Kecha Khampakdee, Juji, Supreme Sundar, Jashwa, Parvez
Co-director: Somaraju PVV
Direction Department : Uday Alla, Aarun Thevar, Lokesh Srinivasan, Kishore Sarella,
Kedar Pashikanti, Durga D.R, Sainadh Alla, Mithilesh Sivagani, Rithica Devireddy,
I.Chaitanya Sravanth, N.Sruti Ranjani, RSN.Roshan Sharif
Chief Associate Editors : Raam tumu, Srinu Bainaboyina
Associate Editors: Prashanth Tej, Yogi (D.F.Tech), Vishnu ramagiri
Executive Producer: Sathyanarayana Guggilla
Production Controller: Manikanta Rongala
Sound Design : Sync Cinema
VFX Supervisor : Raghav Tammareddy
Stills : Mallesh Thatha
Marketing: Walls and Trends
PRO: Venugopal
DI : Annapurna Studios
Marketing : Walls & Trends
Video composition: Walls & Trends
Lyrics -
WASHI YO WASHI 
EAGLE OH EAGLE 

Yasei no washi o korosu ni wa 
To kill a wild Eagle 

Mazu tsubasa o kiri otosu hitsu yoo ga aru 
You need to cut its wings first 

Jimen ni ochitara..me o eguri dasu 
When it falls on the ground you pluck its eyes 

Me ga mienaku nari, doko ni ikeba ii no ka wakara naku suru 
It becomes blind and doesn‚Äôt know where to go 

Sokode ashi o kitte ugokenaku suru 
That‚Äôs when you cut its legs and make it immobile 

Soshite, yasei no shinzou o eguri dasu noda 
And that‚Äôs when you will pluck its wild heart out 

WASHI YO WASHI 
EAGLE O EAGLE

snippet.title: Nallaru Po | Dude | Pradeep Ranganathan | @SaiAbhyankkar | Tippu | Mohit Chauhan | Keerthiswaran
snippet.description:
Presenting the Lyrical Video song of 'Nallaru po' from 'Dude', Written & Directed by Keerthiswaran featuring Pradeep Ranganathan, Mamitha Baiju, R.Sarath Kumar, Hridhu Haroon,Rohini, Aishwarya sharma, Dravid selvam & Others.

An @SaiAbhyankkar  Musical 
Song Title: 'Nallaru po'
Album: Dude

Music Credits:

Composed and produced by @SaiAbhyankkar 
Singers: Tipu , @SaiAbhyankkar  & Mohit Chauhan
Lyricist : Vivek 
Synth ,keys and Bass programmed by @SaiAbhyankkar 
Acoustic ,Electric Bass Guitar & Charango - Keba 
Navtar - Vishnu Ramprasad 
Violin - Chinmayi 
Live Rhythm - Yanka Rhythm group 
Rhythm produced by @SaiAbhyankkar

All recorded and produced at Yolo rechords , engineered by Rajesh Kannan 
Mixed & Masterd by @SaiAbhyankkar

Lyrics:

Nee ketaa unna kooda un kaiyil vittu poguren
Aasa pola vaazhndhukkoyen po
Un mela kaadhal vachene
Thothadhaalum theerala
Ponadhaalum maarala 

Nee ketaa unna kooda un kaiyil vittu poguren
Aasa pola vaazhndhukko di po
Ennalum Kaadhal kuthadhu 
Parvayal Yenga Vechaale 

Paakaama pesaama seraama ponaalum 
Ennaalum nallaru po 
Hey thaangaama thoongaama naan inga vaazhndhaalum
Neeyaachum nallaaru po
 
Kaadhalaa en nenjam
Yekkamaa aanan naane
Kaayamaa nee senjum
Sirikkirene
Yaaradi kutham solla 
En vidhi  enna kolla 
Nee vantha nenjukkulla  
Ippothu onnumilla 

Veroru kayyoda un veral paathen naane 
Vegura nenjoda pogurene
Nethu un kannil naane
Innaikku yaaro dhaane 
Thindaadurene maane
Thaa po nu vittutene 

Paakaama pesaama enkuda seraama ponaalum nallaru po 
Hey thaangaama thoongaama naan inga vaazhndhaalum 
Neeyaachum nallaarupo 

Hey Innoruthanoda nee poga 
Ullolachaloda naan poga 
Enna panna poren Thikku theriyaadhe 
Aanaa neeyum po
 
Hey Ennapanna poren kekaadha
Indha pakkam neeyum paakaadha
Michamulla kaadhal atchadhaya podum 
Nallaa vaazhu po

Presenting the Lyrical Video song of 'Nallaru po' from 'Dude', Written & Directed by Keerthiswaran featuring Pradeep Ranganathan, Mamitha Baiju, R.Sarath Kumar, Hridhu Haroon,Rohini, Aishwarya sharma, Dravid selvam & Others.

An @SaiAbhyankkar  Musical 
Song Title: 'Nallaru po'
Album: Dude

Music Credits:

Composed and produced by @SaiAbhyankkar 
Singers: Tipu , @SaiAbhyankkar  & Mohit Chauhan
Lyricist : Vivek 
Synth ,keys and Bass programmed by @SaiAbhyankkar 
Acoustic ,Electric Bass Guitar & Charango - Keba 
Navtar - Vishnu Ramprasad 
Violin - Chinmayi 
Live Rhythm - Yanka Rhythm group 
Rhythm produced by @SaiAbhyankkar 

Music Supervisor : Sachin Lal
Music consultant : Adesh krishna 
All recorded and produced at Yolo rechords , engineered by Rajesh Kannan 
Mixed & Masterd by @SaiAbhyankkar 

Movie Credits:

Banner: Mythri Movie Makers
Writer & Director: Keerthiswaran
Producers: Naveen Yerneni, Y Ravi shankar

Editing Team: Lokesh Raj, Aathieswaran Rajakumar

Stills: M.Dinesh

PRO: Suresh Chandra, Sathish S2Media
Production Controllers : Rangaraj Perumal, E. Suresh Nambiraj
Marketing: First Show
Lyric Video: ADFX


Lyrics:

Nee ketaa unna kooda un kaiyil vittu poguren
Aasa pola vaazhndhukkoyen po
Un mela kaadhal vachene
Thothadhaalum theerala
Ponadhaalum maarala 

Nee ketaa unna kooda un kaiyil vittu poguren
Aasa pola vaazhndhukko di po
Ennalum Kaadhal kuthadhu 
Parvayal Yenga Vechaale 

Paakaama pesaama seraama ponaalum 
Ennaalum nallaru po 
Hey thaangaama thoongaama naan inga vaazhndhaalum
Neeyaachum nallaaru po
 
Kaadhalaa en nenjam
Yekkamaa aanan naane
Kaayamaa nee senjum
Sirikkirene
Yaaradi kutham solla 
En vidhi  enna kolla 
Nee vantha nenjukkulla  
Ippothu onnumilla 

Veroru kayyoda un veral paathen naane 
Vegura nenjoda pogurene
Nethu un kannil naane
Innaikku yaaro dhaane 
Thindaadurene maane
Thaa po nu vittutene 

Paakaama pesaama enkuda seraama ponaalum nallaru po 
Hey thaangaama thoongaama naan inga vaazhndhaalum 
Neeyaachum nallaarupo 

Hey Innoruthanoda nee poga 
Ullolachaloda naan poga 
Enna panna poren Thikku theriyaadhe 
Aanaa neeyum po
 
Hey Ennapanna poren kekaadha
Indha pakkam neeyum paakaadha
Michamulla kaadhal atchadhaya podum 
Nallaa vaazhu po

snippet.title: PERFECT - Guru Randhawa, Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor | Sunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari
snippet.description:
Sir to pairan de takk,
You so perfect! üíØ

Adding to the fire of ‚ÄòSunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari‚Äô, Guru Randhawa joins the party with PERFECT! üî• Composed and written by Guru Randhawa, Rony Ajnali and Gill Machhrai, the song is sung by Guru Randhawa. Starring our Sunny ‚ÄòVarun Dhawan‚Äô and Tulsi ‚ÄòJanhvi Kapoor‚Äô in the video, get ready to watch, vibe, and replay on loop! üöÄ

#PERFECT #GuruRandhawa #VarunDhawan #janhvikapoor

Dharma Productions & Mentor Disciple Entertainment present 
A Dharma Productions Film
Starring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Sanya Malhotra, & Rohit Saraf

Lyrics:

Sir to pairan de takk
You r so perfect
Pind to shehran de takk
You r so perfect

Kim to v gol lakk
Because You r so perfect
Saare te Tere te jatonde hakk
Because You r so perfect

Sohniye bullan di teri surkhi
Tu patt dita turki
Gall teri turpi

Haye Heer ne a diti tenu gudti
Ni fit Teri kurti
Lata di jiwe murki

Agg lone nakhre ne Patt ta punjab ni
Tuhi kalli dunia te kutt di swaad ni
Tere aage lagde husan saare farzi
Na koi tetho pehla sohni na koi tetho baad ni

Gol gol addian di thakk thakk
You r so perfect
Dressa utte laawe lakh
You r so perfect

Matthe ali teri latt
You r so perfect
Teri juye to v maadi latt
Not so Perfect

Lembo vangu vish vish dharti te ture
Tera Dubbel swing lakk khaye ni
London de sab to mashoor darji to
Gale paan patte ale tu rakaye ni

Akhian to shed shed chakk di nai
Lang jawe Mundyea nu takk di nai
Kade LA kade tu dubai huni ae
Kr kr shoppinga tu thakk di nai

Kacrch di lakh lakh
You r so perfect
Nikl di jach jach
You r so perfect
Teri beauty nu number 10
You r so perfect
Chobaran nu pondi gash
No so perfect

Husna da dang maare Naag di bachi
Toba toba agg kudi banke nachi
Naina ch saroor 7 bottela jinna
Reshami jehe aang odi Umar kachi

Guru nu v maare akh
You r so perfect
Gill Rony laye patt
You r so perfect
Pinda de tu maare jatt
You r so perfect
Tenu maaf ne Qatal 8
Not so perfect

#Vrusshabha #Mohanlal #Diwali2025 #VrusshabhaTeaser #RoarOfVrusshabha #ConnekktMedia #BalajiTelefilms #AbishekSVyasStudios #AashirvadCinemas

Welcome to the World of Vrusshabha.

A unique story brought to life through an unforgettable cinematic experience for global audiences. With Mohanlal playing a king for the very first time in a bilingual epic, Vrusshabha is a film that promises to stay with you long after you leave the theatre. Vrusshabha is a grand Pan Indian film shot simultaneously in Malayalam and Telugu, and dubbed in Hindi and Kannada.


Starring: Mohanlal, Samarjit Lankesh, Ragini Dwivedi

Crew:

Mahalaya, signifies the termination of Pitri Paksha and the beginning of Devi Paksha, thus ushering in the season of religious festivals: It is said that Devi Durga begins her journey from her husband's abode in Kailash to her paternal home on this day: The glory of Durga is known from the ancient treatise Durga Saptasati or the Chandi: It describes the incarnation of Devi Durga by the unification process of all the power of the Gods and her emergence as Mahisasuramardini in the eventual fight with Mahisasura: Recitation of these slokas is known as Chandi Path and has been recited and known to combat every kind of enmity and adversity, from ages forgotten: Since the early 1930s, homes in Bengal reverberate with the immortal verses from Chandi Kabya in the recorded voice of late Birendra Krishna Bhadra: It is a beautiful audio montage of recitation in the enthralling voice of Birendra Krishna Bhadra, Bengali devotional songs with narration scripted by Bani Kumar, classical music composed by Pankaj Kumar Mullick and a dash of acoustic melodrama: Script : Bani Kumar Music Director : Pankaj Kumar Mallick Narration & Chanting of Slokas - Birendra Krishna Bhadra Singers - Supreeti Ghosh, Dwijen Mukherjee, Sumitra Sen, Krishna Dasgupta, Pankaj Mallick, Utpala Sen, Sandhya Mukherjee, Pratima Mukherjee, Tarun Banerjee & Others

Mahalaya, signifies the termination of Pitri Paksha and the beginning of Devi Paksha, thus ushering in the season of religious festivals: It is said that Devi Durga begins her journey from her husband's abode in Kailash to her paternal home on this day: The glory of Durga is known from the ancient treatise Durga Saptasati or the Chandi: It describes the incarnation of Devi Durga by the unification process of all the power of the Gods and her emergence as Mahisasuramardini in the eventual fight with Mahisasura: Recitation of these slokas is known as Chandi Path and has been recited and known to combat every kind of enmity and adversity, from ages forgotten: Since the early 1930s, homes in Bengal reverberate with the immortal verses from Chandi Kabya in the recorded voice of late Birendra Krishna Bhadra: It is a beautiful audio montage of recitation in the enthralling voice of Birendra Krishna Bhadra, Bengali devotional songs with narration scripted by Bani Kumar, classical music composed by Pankaj Kumar Mullick and a dash of acoustic melodrama: Script : Bani Kumar Music Director : Pankaj Kumar Mallick Narration & Chanting of Slokas - Birendra Krishna Bhadra Singers - Supreeti Ghosh, Dwijen Mukherjee, Sumitra Sen, Krishna Dasgupta, Pankaj Mallick, Utpala Sen, Sandhya Mukherjee, Pratima Mukherjee, Tarun Banerjee & Others

Doug (Jack Black) and Griff (Paul Rudd) have been best friends since they were kids, and have always dreamed of remaking their all-time favorite movie: the cinematic "classic" Anaconda. When a midlife crisis pushes them to finally go for it, they head deep into the Amazon to start filming. But things get real when an actual giant anaconda appears, turning their comically chaotic movie set into a deadly situation. The movie they‚Äôre dying to make? It might just get them killed
